*Avioni* su proleteli nad nama. (The planes flew over us.)

Avionima* su potrebne velike količine goriva. (The planes require large amounts of fuel.)

Avionu* je potrebna velika brzina da poleti. (The plane requires a high speed to take off.)

*Avionom* smo stigli u novi grad. (We arrived at a new city by plane.)

*Avionima* je potrebna održavanja da bi leteli. (The planes require maintenance to fly.)